underlying_goal: Update the models used by the 'LLM Council' application.
primary_success: Quickly updated the council models to new frontier models and then correctly reverted ancillary prompt changes when the user changed their mind.
brief_summary: The user requested to update the LLM Council to use newer models and briefly considered making system prompts more rigorous. The agent updated the models, then updated the prompts. The user then asked to undo the prompt changes, which the agent did.
